{"about_the_game":"Inspired by classic RTS games, Flow of War offers a unique Real-Time Strategy (RTS) experience with  Auto-Micro mechanics for both Workers and Warriors. This allows you to concentrate on other aspects of a classic RTS without the need to micromanage individual units.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637210/extras/heading_1.png?t=1728389851\" /><br>Design a well-constructed base not only for good defense but also to allow workers to operate efficiently and perform their tasks in infinitely unique maps.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637210/extras/build.gif?t=1728389851\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637210/extras/defense.gif?t=1728389851\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637210/extras/615_class.png?t=1728389851\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637210/extras/heading_3.png?t=1728389851\" /><br>Embrace the chaos and excitement of battles where multiple units are in action simultaneously.<br><br>Unlike other RTS while you have to micro every single unit, in Flow of War they will fight automatically and you can watch them like it\u2019s Esports!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637210/extras/fight1.gif?t=1728389851\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637210/extras/fight2.gif?t=1728389851\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637210/extras/heading_4.png?t=1728389851\" /><br>Besides inter-racial warfare, you'll also battle with neutral factions to secure key locations, gain rewards and special 